=== 槍暴 ===
他提出{{le|槍支擁有|Gun ownership}}者應需要申請[[牌照|牌照]]。<ref>[https://twitter.com/corybooker/status/1158836715135459328 Twitter] {{Wayback|url=https://twitter.com/corybooker/status/1158836715135459328 |date=20201230220226 }}. 2019-08-07</ref> 在辯論期間，被問到對於[[美國槍械暴力問題|美國槍械暴力問題]]的看法，他回答:

{{quote| 我活在這問題的緊迫感當中，因為當我回[[家|家]] ... 這些{{le|槍聲|gunshot}}每天都真 (I am living with a sense of urgency on this problem because when I go home ... these gunshots, are real every single day)<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cvlrcpZwt3c&t=16s</ref>}}
接受[[電話|電話]][[訪問|訪問]]時，他說：
{{quote| 這些事件以全世界罕見的方式發生 ... 人民能容易地獲得 這些破壞性武器 讓我們變得獨特 (These incidents happen in a way that is unusual in the entire world ... what makes us unique, is the ease with which people can get their hands on these weapons of destruction)<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/corybooker/videos/2702751413079277/ |title=MSNBC |access-date=2019-11-18 |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209200549/https://www.facebook.com/corybooker/videos/2702751413079277/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}
出席[[美国参议院|參議院]]聽證會時，他說：
{{quote| 已死於槍暴的人 多於 我們國家歷史上的每個戰爭 (there are more people that have died of gun violence than in every single war in our nation’s history)<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://newjerseyglobe.com/congress/video-cory-booker-on-shootings-in-colorado-and-georgia/ |title=Video: Cory Booker on shootings in Colorado and Georgia |access-date=2021-04-08 |archive-date=2021-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518235201/https://newjerseyglobe.com/congress/video-cory-booker-on-shootings-in-colorado-and-georgia/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}

